221
00:10:33,899 --> 00:10:35,468
And I think it will.

222
00:10:35,468 --> 00:10:38,971
I'm very encouraged by this
because in the last six years

223
00:10:38,971 --> 00:10:42,108
I think we've done so
much to answer really

224
00:10:42,108 --> 00:10:43,809
a millennia-old problem.

225
00:10:43,809 --> 00:10:45,444
But I think we can
do so much more.

226
00:10:45,444 --> 00:10:47,313
And I think the
momentum is on our side.

227
00:10:47,313 --> 00:10:47,947
Thank you.

